articles.title: 5 years after Britain left the EU, the full impact of Brexit is still emerging - The Associated Press
articles.description: Friday marks five years since Britain left the European Union at 11 p.m. on Jan. 31, 2020. People and businesses are still wrestling with the economic, social and cultural aftershocks of a decision that divided the country. For businesses, Brexit has meant ne…
